     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Given a query\n",
      "\t * what to wear for a casual event\n",
      "And a collection of documents\n",
      "\t * For a casual look  wear jeans and t-shirt\n",
      "\t * For a formal event wear a suit and a tie\n",
      "\t * For a typical smart casual look wear jeans and a shirt \n",
      "And the term-frequency model\n",
      "\t * tf_{i,j}=freq_{i,j}\n",
      "Determine the ranking of documents collection with respect to the given query using a Vector Space Model with the following similarity measures:\n",
      "\t * Euclidean Distance\n",
      "\t * Cosine Similarity\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "q,D=propose_exercize()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 165,
   "metadata": {
    "collapsed": false,
    "scrolled": false
   },
   "outputs": [
    {
